name: This is Not Financial Advice (Self-Reliance)
description:
This HTML file is a proof-of-concept showcasing a "self-contained" html file that doesn't require any external references to function as an animated NFT. A lot of the NFTs that were minted in the 2020s are in danger of "breaking" due to its reliance on traditional web servers to host their images.

This html file is completely self-contained, including the images, stylings, and code itself. It will *always* work, no matter how much time passes through the blockchain.
